isfactory arrangements to repay the debt owed\n\t\t\t to the creditor, a satisfactory statement from the student explaining any\n\t\t\t delinquencies with outstanding balances of less than $2,000, or a\n\t\t\t reduction of the credit requirements under this subsection in response to\n\t\t\t a natural disaster or poor economic conditions that are unforeseen or\n\t\t\t prolonged; and", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subparagraph (B)", "@value": "Higher Education Act of 1965/s:455/ss:r/p:2/sp:B", "@proposed": "true"}], "#text": "shall retain a record of the ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(F)"}, "@id": "H7C06A61B65604F9F8E14FB6DEE450945", "#text": "\n              "}, {"#tail": "\n          ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " determines that a student does not to have an adverse credit\n\t\t\t history in accordance with this subsection, shall consider such\n\t\t\t determination to be in effect for a 2-year period beginning on the date\n\t\t\t the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary", "@entity-id": "9100"}, {"#tail": " makes such determination.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary", "@entity-id": "9100"}], "#text": "in a case in which the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(G)"}, "@id": "H9F2CA73F9DDD46B2866093F4D715C4A9", "#text": "\n              "}]}, {"#tail": "\n        ", "text": {"#tail": "\n          ", "term": {"#tail": " means a graduate or professional student or the parents of a dependent student.", "#text": "student"}, "#text": "For purposes of this subsection, the term "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "(3)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "Definition"}, "#text": "\n            ", "@id": "H5CFA91636C54458FB5A45ACD2951C70F"}], "#text": "\n          ", "@id": "HEBCA8B25BAEE42C3BAD0F905CF031A20"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n